{"TopicId":158292,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"SQUAD hiring banner causes wrong width on mobile","CreatedByName":"Kobymaru","CreatedById":107372,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-27T12:59:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Kobymaru","CreatedById":107372,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-27T12:59:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi! It seems that the \u0022We\u0027re looking for talented developers\u0022 banner is causing some trouble on Mobile.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst, the banner itself is cut off, which wouldn\u0027t be that big of a deal:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/8FGRMVJ\u0022 style=\u0022height:1050px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, the banner causes the site to be bigger than the actual screen size. This also makes the menu on the right partially hidden:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/lSkrtmZ\u0022 style=\u0022height:1050px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut most annoyingly, when scrolled to the right, there is grey \u0022empty\u0022 space:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/ydMhjzN\u0022 style=\u0022height:1050px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that for a forum software that would make a good enough job of mobile-izing the forum just by itself, it\u0027s a bit of a shame that the banner makes things awkward.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any way that this can be fixed so that the site has the proper size on Mobile? Maybe make the banner smaller, or turn it into background?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-27T12:59:50Z\u0022 title=\u002203/27/2017 12:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 27, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Kobymaru\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-28T03:53:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis looks like a job for (I think) \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167672-maneti/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167672\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167672-maneti/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ManeTI\u003C/a\u003E.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ManeTI","CreatedById":167672,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-28T17:38:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi guys, maybe reducing the image size will help, Im going to check with the guys here at the office if its ok to do that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ManeTI","CreatedById":167672,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-28T22:35:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think its good now, can you please confirm? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darth Badie","CreatedById":149302,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-28T22:37:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167672-maneti/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167672\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167672-maneti/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ManeTI\u003C/a\u003E you are awesome !\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-28T22:49:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWidth seems to be okay, I dont have any grey box on the right. \u00A0This is what the banner looks like on my phone (a little small imho):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpo